= Load Sequcense VDBs =
#context: lop

"""Load Sequence VDB file immediately"""

== Overview ==

Create USD layer with Volume and OpenVDB primtive.
filePath properity of OpenVDB primitive will has animated time-sample.

WARNING:
    There in *NO* extent data in primtive (*No Bound info*)

@parameters
Parent Primitive:
    #id: parent_primpath
    The root path of VDB, where Volume will below.
    
Primitive Name:
    #id: prim_name
    The name of Volume primtive, OpenVDB primitive will below it.
    
VDB Files:
    #id: files
    Sequence VDB files
    
Start/End:
    #id: frame_range
    Frame range

Grids:
    #id: grids
    The name of grid will put into OpenVDB primitive. 
    Use space to separate multi-grids.
    
Grid Index:
    #id: grid_index
    Usually 0. Exception in there are multi grids in same name.